structured.title: Ree Confirms Domain Is Set Up Correctly
structured.overview: Ree takes a check-in call from Rachel at Ionos about a recently registered domain. He explains the domain is used as a private internal tool for his church community, hosted on Vercel, and he only needs the domain itself with no public website or additional services. Rachel asks about email needs, but Ree confirms he already uses Google Workspace accounts and does not require Ionos email or further products for this project. Rachel notes this on her system and ends the call amicably.
